            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xACE57C47<!--String: "Everyone knows the Darongs of Dambele as quite the selfless nobles. The amount they've invested on public services and the arts is pretty much unrivaled."--></T>
                  <T>0x882807DC<!--String: "Dambele wasn't always the artistic place it is today, it flourished over generations. The Darongs have been very keen supporters of poetry, painting and all sorts of creative pursuits."--></T>
                  <T>0x7A5C66F7<!--String: "In Dambele, the Darongs are seen as a good, united family. But you know how it is, even the best families have the odd rumor about them."--></T>
                  <T>0x9A765B5F<!--String: "The Hardcover in Dambele is certainly...different. A great place for every generation to meet halfway. Have you tried visiting at night?"--></T>
                  <T>0xB30A4750<!--String: "Dambele's heart is its Community Market. Everyone likes to spend time together there. Gives them sense of belonging."--></T>
                  <T>0xC61C513F<!--String: "The Darongs have always taken such good care of Dambele. Everyone was truly heartbroken after the loss of Jawara's first husband. He was a generous man."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
